milestones.description: Kapil Dev and Yashpal Sharma's 68-run partnership is IND's highest for the 6th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 52 between Kapil Dev and Sandeep Patil
Duleep Mendis and Ranasinghe's 57-run partnership is SL's highest for the 5th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 52 between Pasqual and Duleep Mendis
This is the highest match aggregate (460) involving teams India & Sri Lanka in ODIs
India's 79-run win against Sri Lanka is the largest margin of victory in terms of runs in ODIs, beating 66-run win against Australia
